Description:
   Solar Precision is a passive divine discipline mastered by experienced
   Clerics. Through meditation on Disk's clarity and unwavering judgment,
   the Cleric aligns their divine conduit with solar principles of exactness.
   This alignment improves the critical strike rate of the Cleric's spells,
   allowing their divine attacks to land with far greater force when the
   moment of clarity arrives.

   When Solar Precision triggers, the critical hit also deals bonus damage
   beyond the normal critical multiplier, as the Cleric's perfectly aligned
   divine energy sears through the target with unusual intensity. The
   passive is always active once learned and synergizes with all of the
   Cleric's offensive spell repertoire.
